entry.title: Palace defends Duterte decision to place Cebu City under ECQ | ANC

media:group.media:title: Palace defends Duterte decision to place Cebu City under ECQ | ANC
media:group.media:description:
Placing Cebu City under enhanced community quarantine (ECQ) again is meant to curb the widespread transmission of COVID-19 in the major Visayan city, Malacañang said. Only Cebu City, which was previously under general community quarantine, will be under ECQ until June 30 to control the spread of the disease, Presidential Spokesman Harry Roque said.
